    "As shown in Fig. 16 (in appendix), there is a steady growth of literature focused on the development/application of TM algorithms.",
    "Furthermore, we observed inconsistency in the evaluation metrics used in the literature.",
    "However, topic coherence score, perplexity, diversity, and human evaluation remains the popular metrics.",
    "It is worth stating that a significant number of studies applied TM methods to various domains sub-optimally.",
    "This was also highlighted by prior TM review studies (Asmussen and Møller 2019)."
